<bibRefCitation author="Bailey, R. M. &amp; Bond, C. E." box="[596,868,1807,1834]" pageId="16" pageNumber="517" pagination="1 - 27" refId="ref14835" refString="Bailey, R. M. &amp; Bond, C. E. (1963) Four new species of freshwater sculpins, genus Cottus, from western North America. Occasional Papers of the Museum of Zoology, University of Michigan, 634, 1 - 27." type="journal article" year="1963">Bailey and Bond (1963)</bibRefCitation>
