<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="517">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Girard" baseAuthorityYear="1854" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cottidae" genus="Cottus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpaeniformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="517" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gulosus">C. gulosus</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Diagnostic features are given below.
</paragraph>
